{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2019-09-26-django-custom-response.markdown/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- vim-markdown-toc GFM -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89-django-%E7%9A%84-response\">自定义 django 的 response</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\">实现原理</a>\n* <a href=\"#how-to-use\">How to use</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\">用到的地方</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">普通返回</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%88%86%E9%A1%B5%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">分页返回</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E9%89%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">鉴权返回</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- vim-markdown-toc -->\n<h1 id=\"自定义-django-的-response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89-django-%E7%9A%84-response\" aria-label=\"自定义 django 的 response permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>自定义 django 的 response</h1>\n<h1 id=\"实现原理\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\" aria-label=\"实现原理 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>实现原理</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>status <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> HTTP_200_OK\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>response <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Response\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AttrDict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 将dict的key作为class的属性,可以直接通过.获取熟悉</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__init__<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__dict__ <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CustomResponse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> AttrDict<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">success</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>error <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">False</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Response<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> status<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>HTTP_200_OK<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">fail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>error <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Response<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> status<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>HTTP_200_OK<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"how-to-use\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">In <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>attr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> AttrDict<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nIn <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>attr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\nIn <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>attr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__dict__\nOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nIn <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>attr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"用到的地方\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\" aria-label=\"用到的地方 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>用到的地方</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>view 处理完返回</li>\n<li>分页后返回数据</li>\n<li>自定义权限</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"普通返回\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\" aria-label=\"普通返回 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>普通返回</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>drf api_view</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token decorator annotation punctuation\">@api_view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'GET'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>request<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n email <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>email\n <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> email<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n     cache<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>delete<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n     c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> CustomResponse<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n     c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>token <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span>\n     <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>success<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>drf APIView</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">TestAPIView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>APIView<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  serializer_class <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> TestSerializer\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> request<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>args<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span>kwargs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> CustomResponse<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>message <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'test'</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>success<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>drf ModelViewSet 也是同理,这里就不说了</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"分页返回\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%86%E9%A1%B5%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\" aria-label=\"分页返回 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>分页返回</h2>\n<p>自定义分页，<a href=\"https://www.django-rest-framework.org/api-guide/pagination/#custom-pagination-styles\">官方文档</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> pagination\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> response <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> CustomResponse\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CustomPagination</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pagination<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>PageNumberPagination<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    page_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span>\n    page_size_query_param <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'page_size'</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get_paginated_response</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> CustomResponse<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'data'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'total'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>paginator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>success<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"鉴权返回\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%89%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\" aria-label=\"鉴权返回 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>鉴权返回</h2>\n<p>自定义权限，<a href=\"https://www.django-rest-framework.org/api-guide/permissions/#custom-permissions\">官方文档</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>permissions <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> BasePermission\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exceptions <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> APIException\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> rest_framework<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>status <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> HTTP_200_OK\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">IsLogin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>BasePermission<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">\"\"\"\n    Allows access only to authenticated users.\n    \"\"\"</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">has_permission</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> request<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> view<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> request<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>user<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">raise</span> NeedLogin<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NeedLogin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>APIException<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    status_code <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> HTTP_200_OK\n    default_detail <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'error'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">True</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'请先登录'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    default_code <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'not_authenticated'</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>这个代码片段没有<code class=\"language-text\">CustomResponse</code>, 只能通过使用返回异常, 来保持返回的 response 和之前的返回的格式一致</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89-django-%E7%9A%84-response\">自定义 django 的 response</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\">实现原理</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#how-to-use\">How to use</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\">用到的地方</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">普通返回</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%88%86%E9%A1%B5%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">分页返回</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E9%89%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E\">鉴权返回</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"django custom response","date":"2019-09-26"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019-09-26-django-custom-response.markdown"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"],"slicesMap":{}}